Template: fleet-telemetry/server_host
Type: string
Default: my-domain.com
Description: Enter Fleet Telemetry server hostname

Template: fleet-telemetry/server_port
Type: string
Default: 4443
Description: Enter Fleet Telemetry server port
 Enter Fleet Telemetry server port. This must be accessible from the outside

Template: fleet-telemetry/mqtt_server
Type: string
Default: localhost:1883
Description: Address and port of MQTT broker
 Enter address and port of MQTT broker separated by ':' (colon). The port is usually 1883 for unencrypted connection and 8883 for connection over SSL/TLS